data.description: Introducing a stunning 3 bedroom, 1.75 bath home featuring vaulted ceilings that add a touch of elegance and openness. Experience year-round comfort with ductless heating and AC. Located in the desirable Lake Limerick community, this property offers access to a beautiful lake and its incredible amenities. Relax and entertain on the spacious deck, complete with a luxurious hot tub. The outdoor entertaining space is perfect for hosting gatherings. Plus, enjoy the luxury of a double lot, providing ample room for outdoor activities and expansion. Conveniently park your vehicle in the attached garage. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to call this house your home!
